stanford study of writing about the study methods skip navigation home about the study explore research presentations & publications contact us overview background methods questionnaires interviews longitudinal research research questions acknowledgements methods for our study we began by designing several survey questionnaires an opening demographic questionnaire followed by a series of questionnaires designed to elicit information about student writing practices and attitudes we administered these surveys during each year of the study in addition we carried out interviews with a sub group of students talking with them at length at least once each year and then transcribing the interviews for analysis once data collection was complete we began coding the 15000 texts in our database a process which will take six to eight months finally we will be carrying out textual analyses using methods drawn from rhetorical and discourse analysis in order to complete a number of case studies of participant writers 2008 stanford study of writing contact us
